You need an .iso burning program like nero / sonic mydvd / or alcohol 120 to burn the images onto dvd.  Either that, or you could use a program called Daemon Tools (free download from their website) to "mount" the .iso file.  This makes the computer think a dvd with this image is in the drive and plays it.
